  <section id="about">
    <h2>About ELHAM</h2>
    <p><strong>ELHAM</strong> stands for <em>Empowering Learning through Holistic Advancement and Mentorship</em>. We equip individuals with the knowledge and skills they need, addressing personal, professional, and institutional growth through mentorship and continuous support.</p>

    <h3>Vision</h3>
    <p>ELHAM envisions a resilient, knowledgeable, and self-reliant society where individuals and institutions thrive through inclusive and transformative learning. We strive to become a leading consultancy in Afghanistan and the region by delivering innovative, culturally relevant, and high-impact training and mentorship solutions.</p>

    <h3>Mission</h3>
    <p>Our mission is to deliver accessible, high-quality, and context-driven training and capacity-building programs that empower individuals, organizations, and communities. We specialize in project and financial management, taxation, monitoring and evaluation, humanitarian response, and digital literacy. Through a learner-centered approach and evidence-based methods, we aim to bridge knowledge gaps and promote sustainable growth.</p>
  </section>

